{
  "stem": "6257.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then this family, the Serafins, Jan and Krisya were there names, and the child.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they jumped off with me, and some other people jumped off.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I don't think the Germans cared that much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we walked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The had family in their place, called [INAUDIBLE], called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think, where there was a whole family, a whole village, more or less, of people with their surname, called the Serafins.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I-- we just walked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there we got and-- and stayed in this village in a little hut, a little wooden hut with-- with the family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somehow they let us stay there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They-- and we ate whatever little food they had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So that was by that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I suppose October.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some relations.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not-- in some [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think that he called her an aunt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know if she was actually his aunt or-- and they used to go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is [INAUDIBLE] Serafin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The man who-- with whom I stayed was [INAUDIBLE] he and his wife used to go to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Walked, it was about 30 miles, I should imagine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And find things and sort of sell some things of people who either had left or were killed or something and then bring it and sell it on the market, and the market.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the village was so poor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was-- you know, after all that I had been through, I was surprised, suddenly, at Warsaw, that they'd never seen electricity.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, they had a well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they couldn't read and it was just that the-- it was such a different life, not completely self-sufficient.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, because of the war, they made their own clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was winter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, you know, the animals lived in the hut with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
